<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n05009c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05009c">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05009c"> 9(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> &mdash; fasts on Trian!</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Patrick complained to a chief named Trian about the cruelty with which he treated his slaves.]</font> Finding, however, that words failed, the Saint sat down at <mark>Trian&apos;s gate, and &ldquo;fasted upon him,&rdquo;</mark> remaining there for a long time without food <small> William Bullen Morris, <a name="WBML" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WBML"><cite title="source">The Life of Saint Patrick Apostle of Ireland</cite></a>, 4th ed. (1890) 249</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
